headline: Baron Durable Advantage Fund Bets on Danaher Corporation (DHR) During Cyclical Challenges
summary: Baron Fund, an investment management company, released its Q4 2025 letter for “Baron Durable Advantage Fund”. A copy of the letter can be downloaded here. The Fund returned 2.6% in the fourth quarter, which mirrored the S&P 500 Index’s 2.7% return. The Fund returned 16.6% in 2025, compared to 17.9% for the Index and 16.1% gain […]
